Package project.star_wars_universe.cli.commands

Class CommandsList

java.lang.Object
project.star_wars_universe.cli.commands.CommandsList
All Implemented Interfaces:
PlanetsRepositoryObserver
public class CommandsList extends Object implements PlanetsRepositoryObserver
A singleton class which is responsible for adding, removing, initializing and providing of all the commands of the application. It is also an observer of the PlanetsRepository class.

    • onPlanetAdded

      public void onPlanetAdded(Planet planet)
      When a Planet is added to the PlanetsRepository, this method adds a new instance of the PrintCombinedPlanetsInfo command to the commands map for the new planet. This is necessary because when the user enters a command in the console, only the first segment of the input is used to find the corresponding Command handler in the commands map. (e.g. when the user enters "Naboo + Dagobah", "Naboo" is considered as the String for invoking a command in the CLI).
      Specified by:
      onPlanetAdded in interface PlanetsRepositoryObserver
      Parameters:
      planet - the new Planet added to the PlanetsRepository.

    • onPlanetRemoved

      public void onPlanetRemoved(Planet planet)
      When a Planet is removed from the PlanetsRepository, this method removes the PrintCombinedPlanetsInfo command from the commands map corresponding to the removed planet.
      Specified by:
      onPlanetRemoved in interface PlanetsRepositoryObserver
      Parameters:
      planet - the Planet removed to the PlanetsRepository.
